{"tid":898984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎紀念一戰結束百年活動 遇半裸女權分子示威","createTime":"2018-11-12T05:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T09:07:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7d18372084c996364ab9170581be8c91dccdb3","tid":898984,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw7WoAA3sKD.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDroayw7WoAA3sKD.jpg&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bf84771e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw7WoAA3sKD.jpg</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">女權組織FEMAN在凱旋門示威，諷刺多國為一戰戰犯、獨裁者。FEMAN Twitter</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正當世界領袖雲集法國巴黎出席紀念第一次世界大戰結束100周年活動之際，以無上裝示威聞名的烏克蘭激進女權組織FEMEN，3名裸露上身的女成員周六在巴黎凱旋門前示威，被警員強行拉走。<br />\n<br />\n3人在約70名領袖周日出席紀念活動的凱旋門前，高舉示威標語，寫上「歡迎戰犯」的口號，明顯諷刺美國總統特朗普、德國總理默克爾等世界領袖。她們又在身上寫上「真正獨裁者」、「偽和平締造者」和「戰犯」等字句。她們的標語又噴上假血作為特效。3人的舉動吸引大批途人圍觀。但警方很快便上前干預，把3人強行拖走。<br />\n<br />\nFEMEN組織向以裸胸抗議聞名國際，經常舉行各式各樣的示威。今年7月，該組織其中1名創辦人夏科（Oksana Shachko）被發現倒斃巴黎寓所，終年31歲。當局其後證實是自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n夏科去世前在巴黎以「政治避難」身份生活，她留下一封政治性極強的遺書，譴責社會和男人的虛偽。夏科此前曾經幾次自殺不遂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw8XQAE_m3C.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDroayw8XQAE_m3C.jpg&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d5d351ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw8XQAE_m3C.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw8WwAEacZ_.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDroayw8WwAEacZ_.jpg&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d59f6744\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw8WwAEacZ_.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/861781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F861781&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ce69e067\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F861781&h=3eb65086\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/861781</a>"},{"pid":"6ba09bc2e8826bab3a5756ba4e8a8b4b82d15cc2","tid":898984,"uid":35870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123ae70e7fe4fe65f9c64b6e368bd628bd99cf88","tid":898984,"uid":32282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f55554cbd57e76d5892f792bb0525cf42de8d6c","tid":898984,"uid":3117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"對波細左d"},{"pid":"e30304fd276ed86f7c53a1a8d861db02f3fd92b1","tid":898984,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ba6cdc930502e69533eb6650a00ce0fab71f31","tid":898984,"uid":221773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:41:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw7WoAA3sKD.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDroayw7WoAA3sKD.jpg&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bf84771e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Droayw7WoAA3sKD.jpg</a><br />\n中間嗰個正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif